Package: tweetio
Title: Really, Really, Ridiculously Fast Tweet Data
Version: 0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Brendan", "Knapp", 
           email = "brendan.g.knapp@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3284-4972"))
Description: 
    `{tweetio}`'s goal is to go from raw tweets to `{rtweet}`-style data frames 
    as fast as possible, whether or not the data came from the Twitter API, a 
    database dump, or some other library.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.3)
SystemRequirements: zlib, C++11
